    <title>Python 学习笔记 2</title>
    <link href="https://peihaibin.github.io/2017/09/25/Python-%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0-2/"/>
    <id>https://peihaibin.github.io/2017/09/25/Python-学习笔记-2/</id>
